      <note id="note_x43_fpz_5gc" type="note" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">If a fuse filament separates, use only the same type and size fuses for replacement. If the
        filament in a new fuse separates. Have the circuits and instruments checked.</p>
      </note>
      <note id="note_dgc_gpz_5gc" type="notice" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Always replace fuses with ones of the correct ampere rating.</p>
      </note>
